---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Picture } from '@astrojs/image/components';
import cheryl from '../images/cheryl.png';
import latte from '../images/latte.png';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <div
    id="about"
    class="about flex p-8 md:p-16 md:pt-32 align-center flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start"
  >
    <div class="md:mr-16 md:w-1/2 w-full">
      <Picture
	class="w-full"
	src={cheryl}
	alt="cheryl"
	widths={[800, 600, 800]}
	sizes="100%"
	aspectRatio={800 / 500}
	fit="cover"
      />
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col justify-center md:text-left md:items-start items-center text-center basis-full md:w-2/5 md:basis-2/5"
    >
      <h1 class="font-serif my-4 font-medium text-5xl">
	About Lavender Health
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg leading-loose">
	Lavender Health is led by Cheryl Tan APRN. Cheryl is a compassionate
	medical professional and a leading expert in her field. She has over 16
	years of experience as a nurse practitioner and she is double board
	certified. She earned her Master of Science in Family Health Nursing
	from Wichita State University and later obtained her Master of Science
	in Psychiatric Mental Health Nursing from Washburn University. She is
	board certified by AANP and ANCC. She is extremely knowledgeable about
	medication evaluation and management, ensuring that every patient is on
	the proper medication. She will also treat each patient with dignity and
	compassion. She also has Latte her helpful goldendoodle who enjoys
	seeing patients with her.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="about flex p-8 md:p-16 md:pt-32 align-center flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start"
  >
    <div
      class="flex flex-col justify-center md:text-left md:items-start items-center text-center basis-full md:w-2/5 md:basis-2/5"
    >
      <p class="text-lg leading-loose">
	Cheryl treats a variety of diagnosis include Major Depression, Anxiety,
	Bipolar, Schizophrenia, ADHD, Binge eating disorder, insomnia. She can
	also help with patients struggling with their weight and desiring weight
	loss. She works with patients 7 years and up. If you would like Cheryl
	to evaluate your medication regimen, please schedule an appointment with
	her. She sees patients in person and virtually. She accepts most types
	of commercial insurance, as well as Medicare and Medicaid.
      </p>
      <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="md:ml-16 md:w-1/2 w-full">
      <Picture
	class="w-full"
	src={latte}
	alt="latte"
	widths={[800, 600, 800]}
	sizes="100%"
	aspectRatio={800 / 500}
	fit="cover"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
<style>
.about {
  background-color: #EFEFEF;
}
</style>
